html:
I have been following a new e-mail service provider called Protonmail for quite some time, and I think it would be beneficial for an awesome project like TOS to add a TOS;DR review for it. 

  • Here is the URL to the Protonmail homepage: https://protonmail.com 
  • URL for Protonmail Terms of Service: https://protonmail.com/terms-and-conditions
  • Protonmail Privacy Agreement: https://protonmail.com/privacy-policy 

Regards,

-- Kevin
